All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    application is responsible for inspecting and evaluating tasks for students.
    DslParser
    utility class for parsing DSL configurations using Groovy.
    GitManager
    utility class for managing Git repositories.
    GradleController
    utility class for inspecting Gradle tasks in project.
    GroovySupport
    configurable class for handling Groovy scripts.
    Group
    represents group contains list of students.
    HtmlReportConstructor
    utility class for generating HTML reports using Freemarker templates.
    Student
    represents student with identifier, full name and repository information.
    StudentTask
    represents task assigned to student with various attributes indicating task's status and evaluation results.
    Task
    represents task with various attributes such as identifier, name, deadlines, maximum points and progress of student tasks.
    TestConfiguration
    represents configuration for tests, containing information about tasks, groups, handouts, checkpoints and seminars.
